<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[Image:Part_Measure_Toggle_Delta.svg|32px]] [[Part_Measure_Toggle_Delta|Toggle Delta]]: Shows or hides delta measurements. Not available in {{VersionPlus|1.0}}.
</div>

